* Origin Story: The brand "isn't a marketing pitch‚Äîit's the origin story of a weapon." It was born from "years... in the trenches, navigating the fog of psychological attrition." ("The Genesis of RyanrealAF") The "realAF" is "the raw, unedited footage from the front lines," while "The Game Unseen" is "the cold, hard analysis‚Äîthe blueprint of the battlefield." ("The Genesis of RyanrealAF")
